name: Star wars rebel pilot suit(cockpit view update)
description:
The models are close to generating those suits, but without a lora i couldnt get the iconic look. So i made this one.

You can try to force the helmet on by adding "with helmet on" in the prompt

You can now alo create cockpit view. Add "cockpit view" to the prompt to trigger it. It helps to add "helmet on" and "googles on".

The suits should still generate fine, but if you dont need cockpit view then its ok to use V0.1
